    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade specimen featuring the legendary S54B32 high-revving inline-six. The VANOS system has been fully overhauled with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates to ensure long-term structural integrity. The Getrag Type D six-speed manual gearbox is paired with a fresh Sachs clutch, delivering linear power to the factory limited-slip differential. The exterior paint presents with exceptional clarity and consistent depth across all panels, while the interior's Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear or UV degradation. This vehicle has undergone a recent Valve Adjustment and Rod Bearing service, verified by oil analysis, making it a mechanically flawless, turnkey investment for the discerning collector.",
